            <p class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">The commercial poultry industry is built on a sophisticated breeding pyramid that efficiently multiplies superior genetic traits from a few elite birds to millions of production animals.</p>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
